Enhancements to update API (00E-011)
Enhancements to update API (00E-011)
Enhancement to /update:
Update sale invoice for cases where BNP generates invoice (e.g. in case of F&B ISN) (00E);
Update delivery address (00F);
Update pickup authorization (for "Buyer-Delivery"), delivery authorization (other fulfillment types, i.e. "Delivery", "Self-Pickup") (010);
Update instructions for delivery (011):
fulfillment.end.instructions can be used by buyer to communicate additional info for delivery e.g.:
long_desc - for sending specific instructions such as "leave package outside door";
additional_desc - for sending additional information including visual or textual information related to delivery;
Can also be sent in /confirm and updated here;
Enhancement to /on_update:
Order price adjustment (post-confirmation), not tied to return or cancellation (012);
will be in the form of price reduction, for 1 or more items, in the order;
can be unsolicited, in the form of "quote_update" fulfillment, with quote_trail having breakup of delta changes in price, with updated quote; this fulfillment will also be linked to the forward fulfillment(s) of the items for which delta price change has been applied;
can be applied before order reaches terminal state of "Completed" or "Cancelled";
Update self-pickup instructions (013):
fulfillment.start.instructions can be used by seller to communicate additional info for pickup, e.g.:
long_desc - for sending register / counter no for rider / buyer (Self-Pickup);
additional_desc - for sending additional information including visual or textual information related to pickup (Self-Pickup);
Can also be sent in /on_confirm and updated here;
